{
  "texts": [
    "Diagnostic scans play an equal role in the detection of disease, earlier models focused on MRI image data for classification.",
    "Sivakani and Ansari (2020) proposed a ML framework for AD diagnosis.",
    "The ML algorithm is utilized for both feature selection and extraction, followed by classification on the OASIS longitudinal dataset.",
    "EM algorithm is used for clustering.",
    "Best First Search (BFS) is utilized for selecting the features."
  ]
}